episodes.title: Psychedelic Assisted Therapy
episodes.plot: Coming back from the break, John Oliver explains the long trend of fear-mongering about the psychedelic treatments. He discusses about psychedelic assisted therapy and its history, how it got here, its potentials, and future possibilities. But it will require cautious monitoring to reap the benefits psychedelic treatments without someone getting hurt.

episodes.title: Artificial Intelligence
episodes.plot: Artificial intelligence has tremendous potential as it is increasingly becoming part of our lives, from used in cell phones to ChatGPT. John Oliver discusses how these AI works is a mystery, how it is being used in the wrong way, why it needs to be closely looked at, where it might be heading next in future.

episodes.title: Ron DeSantis
episodes.plot: Ron DeSantis, the governor of Florida is the centerpiece of discussion republican community. But John Oliver discusses how he is not less formidable than the infamous Donald Trump. He also points out the way he runs things in the free state and why it is bad for the society.

episodes.title: TANF
episodes.plot: John Oliver discusses the federal assistance program namely Temporary Assistance for Needy Families (TANF) which is designed to help needy families with little to no income. He points out how these fund is being handled, who are really getting benefited and how the less fortunate people are being deprived of their essentials for basic living.

episodes.title: Timeshares
episodes.plot: John Oliver discusses timeshares, how people get into them, why it's so difficult to get out, and one exciting new business venture.

episodes.title: Solitary Confinement
episodes.plot: John Oliver discusses solitary confinement which was called different names in different places due to the bad reputation it consists. Nevertheless, whatever is the name is the effect is equally dire on the inmates. He talks about how harmful it is, history of it, and what steps are needed to be taken to improve the situation.

episodes.title: HOAs
episodes.plot: John Oliver discusses about HOAs (homeowners associations) influences in American society. He talks about the ridiculous amount of power they have with little to none accountability and government's unwillingness to help the people in need by saying literally 'Good Luck'.

episodes.title: Farmworkers
episodes.plot: John Oliver introduced the less discussed part of the farming in America. Who are the farm-workers mainly and what is the conditions their work. He discusses why everyone failed to protect them, and the basic things needs to be fulfilled without delay for them.

episodes.title: Cryptocurrencies II
episodes.plot: John Oliver discusses cryptocurrency in a new installment. He discusses three segments of the cryptoverse: Crypto coins which are made-up, Crypto banks seems like a ponzi scheme and Crypto exchanges working as embezzlement. He also points out that they did with the building false confidence to the general people.

episodes.title: Biden and the Border
episodes.plot: John Oliver discusses the border issues of United States of America and the things President Biden promised to fix those issues but did not deliver yet. He also criticizes the new app which was introduced by the President to help the asylum seekers.
